Kup(via comm): Understood Aerotaur. Kup out.
Kup closed the channel and continued on his way. As he was waiting for Condor to report he got an idea. He opens a channel to Flicker. He was sure that Flicker was not who he said he was now and decides that he can play some mind games.
Kup(via comm): Flicker, I know what your up to. Give it up. You'll never get out fo the base.
 Rudra656@... wrote:::Aerotaur:: 
      "Er, I'd love to help sir, but I've got to watch their baby for the time being.  I just wouldn't feel right leaving it here alone.  I'm sure there are others in the base who can find them."  He sighs and closes the comlink to walk over to baby Elita.  "I think you're mom's in a lot of trouble.  But I'm sure she'll be okay."  He picks her up again and rocks her in his arms.
